    "Convergence in response rankings could be elicited following a Delphi style procedure such as the one performed in IPCC AR6 (Zommers et al. 2020).",
    "Moreover, the performance of the technology can be improved by using sensibly curated corpora.",
    "These corpora can in principle be tailored to specific topics as, for example adaptation (Sietsma et al. 2024a, b), where using AI allows for small teams of authors (e.g.",
    "authors of IPCC special reports or chapter authors) to develop queries tailored to the information they are interested in (De-Gol et al. 2023).",
